			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just an observation.  Quickened summoning gets capped at 50%.
<br />

<br />
QS2                         =25%
<br />
Focus ring                = 15%
<br />
Blessing of Rev/Faith = 10%
<br />

<br />
Total                        = 50%
<br />

<br />
You can, if you wish, save some AA points by not going all the way to QS3.
<br />

<br />
