				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">First Aid</span> 1/1/1 - Allows you to bind wound higher than normal (10% per level). Most useful for bind wounding other players, however. When self binding, the magician loses several hp/tic and is not meditating.
<br />

<br />
I have thought to get this discipline even before regeneration after RS III, considering our endless supply of bandages. In regard to the lost hp/tic, what if I am mounted?</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
